<h2 style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #3A5A40; margin: 0 0 4px 0;">
  Monthly Progress — {{monthName}} {{year}} 📈
</h2>
<p style="color: #888; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 28px 0;">Here's a look at your spiritual activity this month.</p>

<p>Hi <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>
  You're making great progress! Here's your Spiriment summary for
  <strong>{{monthName}} {{year}}</strong>. Keep it up — consistency is where growth happens.
</p>

<!-- Stats grid: use table for email client compatibility -->
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 28px 0;">
  <tr>
    <td width="48%" style="background: #f3f7f4; border-left: 4px solid #3A5A40; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 18px; vertical-align: top;">
      <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Days Read</div>
      <div style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: #3A5A40;">{{totalDaysRead}}</div>
    </td>
    <td width="4%"></td>
    <td width="48%" style="background: #f3f7f4; border-left: 4px solid #3A5A40; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 18px; vertical-align: top;">
      <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Reading Minutes</div>
      <div style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: #3A5A40;">{{totalReadingMinutes}}</div>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr><td colspan="3" style="height: 12px;"></td></tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="48%" style="background: #f3f7f4; border-left: 4px solid #3A5A40; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 18px; vertical-align: top;">
      <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Longest Streak</div>
      <div style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: #3A5A40;">{{longestStreak}} days 🔥</div>
    </td>
    <td width="4%"></td>
    <td width="48%" style="background: #f3f7f4; border-left: 4px solid #3A5A40; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 18px; vertical-align: top;">
      <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Sessions Completed</div>
      <div style="font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: #3A5A40;">{{sessionsCount}}</div>
    </td>
  </tr>
  {{#if topBook}}
  <tr><td colspan="3" style="height: 12px;"></td></tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="3" style="background: #f3f7f4; border-left: 4px solid #3A5A40; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 18px;">
      <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Top Book</div>
      <div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #3A5A40;">{{topBook}}</div>
      {{#if topBookChapters}}
      <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #888; margin-top: 4px;">{{topBookChapters}} chapters read</div>
      {{/if}}
    </td>
  </tr>
  {{/if}}
</table>

<p style="color: #555; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; border-top: 1px solid #EBEEEC; padding-top: 20px;">
  "Your word is a lamp for my feet, a light on my path." — Psalm 119:105
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0 8px 0;">
  <a href="spiriment://reports" class="button">View Full Report in App</a>
</div>

<p>Keep going, {{userName}} — you're doing amazing. 🌿</p>

<p>Warm regards,<br /><strong>The Spiriment Team</strong></p>
